    "displayName": "Visits",
    "summary": "The visits feature manages the full lifecycle of veterinary visit records, exposing REST endpoints on visits-service to create and retrieve visits per pet, backed by a JPA repository and visits database table. It is surfaced to end users through the api-gateway's owner-details aggregation flow, where visit data for all of an owner's pets is fetched in bulk and merged with customer information behind a circuit breaker."
