    "narrative": "A client requests owner details via GET /api/gateway/owners/{ownerId} on the ApiGatewayController, which reactively fans out to two downstream services. CustomersServiceClient fetches the owner profile (including their pets) from customers-service, while VisitsServiceClient — protected by a circuit breaker — calls VisitResource on visits-service with the extracted pet IDs. VisitResource delegates to VisitRepository, which issues a bulk SQL query against the visits table. The gateway then merges the owner profile with the returned Visits collection and returns a fully enriched OwnerDetails response to the caller.",
